      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS system. The chassis has been addressed with rear subframe reinforcement, and the 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides precise engagement. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and fresh fluids for the limited-slip differential. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust, delivering linear power and sharp handling characteristics. A well-maintained driver's car for the purist seeking analog feedback.",
