      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a beautifully maintained sedan in Midnight Blue Metallic that strikes the perfect balance between executive luxury and daily practicality. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, with only minor stone chips on the front bumper and hood consistent with responsible highway driving. The body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are free of major curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring charcoal leather upholstery that remains supple; there is very light wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster, but the passenger and rear seats appear nearly new. All technological features, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and the touchscreen infotainment system, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and pulls cleanly through all gears. This vehicle has been serviced exclusively at authorized centers, with a recent oil change and a fresh set of premium all-season tires just installed. It is a turn-key vehicle that offers a smooth, rattle-free driving experience for its next owner.",
